lines.text: From: Southwest Ontario Aboriginal Health Access Centre-Chippewa
Re: Daniel (Danny) Antone May 31, 1971 Age: 54 yr HN: 5501 846 330 EA
PUD with duodenal ulcer Dr Black 2022
Ventolin HFA 100 mcg/actuation 2 inhalations every 4 hours, PRN for 14 days
multivitamin 1 tab 1 tablet 1 time daily for 3 months of 28 days
Nasonex 50 mcg/actuation 2 sprays 2 times daily for 30 days
polysaccharide iron complex 150 mg iron 1 capsule every 2 days for 3 months of
28 days Feramax. Take in evening on empty stomach, away from other meds.
calcium carbonate 1000 mg 1 time daily for 3 months of 28 days
Tinactin 1 % 1 application 2 times daily for 28 days apply to groin
cholecalciferol (vitamin d3) 2,000 unit (50 mcg) 1 capsule 1 time daily for 28 days
thiamine hol (vitamin b1) 100 mg 1 tablet 1 time daily for 3 months of 28 days
alendronate 70 mg 1 time weekly for 12 weeks take with full glass of water on
empty stomach away from other medications
ACETAMINOPHEN 500 MG TABLET 2 tablets 3 times daily, PRN
clotrimazole 1 % 1 application 2 times daily for 14 days use twice daily until one
week after rash resolves then continue with tinactin spray
